    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<i><strong>Berry</strong></i> is a short orthogonal 3D platformer centered on delivering light bullet-hell challenges and precise projectile manipulation using its unique web-orbiting systems. Fight unique bosses and unlock new abilities in this tiny Metroidvania adventure!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823370/extras/73ed09fb379adaa35148da671a18c78d.poster.avif?t=1681232404\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823370/extras/73ed09fb379adaa35148da671a18c78d.webm?t=1681232404\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823370/extras/73ed09fb379adaa35148da671a18c78d.mp4?t=1681232404\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome! Welcome!</h2>Embark on a small and crunchy adventure up <i>Yamakuu</i> mountain's somewhat treacherous terrain to reach an illumination brighter than any spider has ever achieved. Explore over <strong>50 maps</strong> and combat multiple bosses while platforming, dodging, and vibing within the world of bugs. Try and consume all the flies hidden throughout the world!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823370/extras/6497c962a9682b9465a2a3dffffdc77f.poster.avif?t=1681232404\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823370/extras/6497c962a9682b9465a2a3dffffdc77f.webm?t=1681232404\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823370/extras/6497c962a9682b9465a2a3dffffdc77f.mp4?t=1681232404\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >New Features!</h2>As the 1st place winner of the Touch the Stars game jam, Berry was already packed with tons of challenging and unique platforming mechanics; however, upon being published to Steam, Berry has been updated with new features based on user feedback!<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Collect hundreds of NOMI spread across the world to spend on newly added shops!<br>    </li><li>Track down each of the 4 terrains’ shops, each with unique items that provide new combat, cosmetic, and utility capabilities to your tiny spider!<br>    </li><li>Make use of the new shield system! Either use the shields to provide yourself with additional health or find methods to dispose and gain more NOMI!<br>    </li><li>There are now a total of 20 flies hidden in the world! The more you collect, the more powerful your abilities become.<br>    </li><li>Added a complete options menu and the ability to reference the game controls from the pause menu.</li></ul> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823370/extras/c197c7be4c0655dc26ff2822a908bbe7.poster.avif?t=1681232404\" width=600 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823370/extras/c197c7be4c0655dc26ff2822a908bbe7.webm?t=1681232404\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823370/extras/c197c7be4c0655dc26ff2822a908bbe7.mp4?t=1681232404\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiple Endings!</h2>Depending on the number of flies that are collected and consumed, the game may end with any of the 5 available endings (with a 6th true ending that requires additional conditions to be fulfilled). Will you remain a weak spider for the sake of the mindless flies? Or will you consume everything in your path and become an unstoppable force?<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823370/extras/f66042027a6650c1630146ae488190fc.poster.avif?t=1681232404\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823370/extras/f66042027a6650c1630146ae488190fc.webm?t=1681232404\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823370/extras/f66042027a6650c1630146ae488190fc.mp4?t=1681232404\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
